2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses the failure of DNNs to generalize to OoD inputs, which is a common problem in AI. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses DNNs and investigates their behavior, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper uses 3D renderers and models to investigate the vulnerability of DNNs, which is related to computer graphics. 
5. cs.GRAPHICS (Computer Graphics) - The paper uses 3D renderers and models extensively to investigate the vulnerability of DNNs, which is related to computer graphics.
